      • clearCacheEntriesForContact

        public static void clearCacheEntriesForContact(ABContact contact)
        Clears any DiffDisplays for PendingUpdates for the contact passed in from the DiffDisplay cache. This should be called when a contact changes in the database which may require the PendingUpdate DiffDisplay to be recomputed.
        Parameters:
        contact - - the contact which has changed
